  <source>Samsung Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the efficacy and toxicity of different timing of
      concurrent chemoradiation in the treatment of limited disease status Small-cell lung cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
